{"tid":689154,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"電腦分析　皇馬新帥70%係肥沙","createTime":"2018-06-04T01:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T05:32:04.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c43b7def57486a9ba507f2d6d332103675c7d64e","tid":689154,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T01:08:57.000Z","msg":"施丹辭職之後，皇馬新帥人選眾說紛紜，包括雲格、古迪、普捷天奴，但根據意大利傳媒《CalcioNapoli24》爆料，前拿玻里教練沙利有70%機會成為「新艦長」。 <br />\n<br />\n皇馬原本頭號目標係熱刺領隊普捷天奴，但由於佢剛續約冇幾耐，熱刺又唔肯放人，挖角成功機會非常低，於是轉向沙利埋手。《CalcioNapoli24》引述消息人士，指沙利70%機會加盟皇馬。 <br />\n<br />\n本來車路士可以優先簽沙利，但由於拒絕賠償800萬鎊畀拿玻里，令談判破裂。呢條數對於皇馬只係濕濕碎，要簽入沙利並唔難。"},{"pid":"5eacd8bc320961d423b71010bc8da741bb9a65c5","tid":689154,"uid":111425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:51:33.000Z","msg":"我轟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc5dba3c9d2d4b39e86635e8e5428691371279e","tid":689154,"uid":8392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T02:53:20.000Z","msg":"壓唔壓得住d球星呀？"},{"pid":"df66726fbd4954b9e1d0781bf930a40b32265492","tid":689154,"uid":8000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"資料顯示<br />\n有65%係肥沙 30%係雲加 <br />\n唔係肥沙就係雲加<br />\n都唔係就其他"},{"pid":"37e7ceeacf67495abbd7d3243d6f06638b568ffa","tid":689154,"uid":28378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df66726fbd4954b9e1d0781bf930a40b32265492","tid":689154,"uid":8000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T03:04:21.000Z","msg":"資料顯示<br />\n有65%係肥沙 30%係雲加 <br />\n唔係肥沙就係雲加<br />\n都唔係就其他"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:36:55.000Z","msg":"開個肥普被佢，等佢贏巴1分"},{"pid":"11456917bc5f542bd2d5c60e95651a8b1fd17820","tid":689154,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37e7ceeacf67495abbd7d3243d6f06638b568ffa","tid":689154,"uid":28378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df66726fbd4954b9e1d0781bf930a40b32265492","tid":689154,"uid":8000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"s